#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.xs.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.xs"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:1 of
msgid "Return cross-section from the Series/DataFrame."
msgstr "从 Series/DataFrame 返回交叉部分。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:3 of
msgid ""
"This method takes a `key` argument to select data at a particular level "
"of a MultiIndex."
msgstr "此方法使用 `key` 参数来选择 MultiIndex 的特定级别的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:6 of
msgid "Label contained in the index, or partially in a MultiIndex."
msgstr "索引中包含的标签，或部分在 MultiIndex 中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:8 of
msgid "Axis to retrieve cross-section on."
msgstr "用于检索交叉部分的轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:10 of
msgid ""
"In case of a key partially contained in a MultiIndex, indicate which "
"levels are used. Levels can be referred by label or position."
msgstr ""
"如果 key 部分包含在 MultiIndex 中，则指示使用哪些级别。级别可以通过标签或"
"位置引用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:13 of
msgid "If False, returns object with same levels as self."
msgstr "如果为 False，则返回与自身具有相同级别的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:16 of
msgid ""
"Cross-section from the original Series or DataFrame corresponding to the "
"selected index levels."
msgstr "来自原始 Series 或 DataFrame 的交叉部分，对应于选定的索引级别。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:23 of
msgid "Access a group of rows and columns by label(s) or a boolean array."
msgstr "通过标签或布尔数组访问一组行和列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.iloc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:26 of
msgid "Purely integer-location based indexing for selection by position."
msgstr "基于纯整数位置的索引，用于按位置选择。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:30 of
msgid "`xs` can not be used to set values."
msgstr "`xs` 不能用于设置值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:32 of
msgid ""
"MultiIndex Slicers is a generic way to get/set values on any level or "
"levels. It is a superset of `xs` functionality, see :ref:`MultiIndex "
"Slicers <advanced.mi_slicers>`."
msgstr ""
"MultiIndex Slicers 是一种通用方法，可在任意级别上获取/设置值。它是 `xs` "
"功能的超集，请参见 :ref:`MultiIndex Slicers <advanced.mi_slicers>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:38 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:55 of
msgid "Get values at specified index"
msgstr "获取指定索引处的值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:64 of
msgid "Get values at several indexes"
msgstr "获取多个索引处的值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:71 of
msgid "Get values at specified index and level"
msgstr "获取指定索引和级别的值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:78 of
msgid "Get values at several indexes and levels"
msgstr "获取多个索引和级别的值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.xs.xs:86 of
msgid "Get values at specified column and axis"
msgstr "获取指定列和轴的值"

